    {"type":"text","id":"comp_h","x":10,"y":46,"width":490,"height":18,"text":"COMPONENTES OBLIGATORIOS","originalText":"COMPONENTES OBLIGATORIOS","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#064e3b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":211,"version":1,"versionNonce":212,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"comp_c","x":18,"y":68,"width":474,"height":212,"text":"① Dataset y Datos\n   • Fuente: OpenCL Benchmark Suite v2.1 (acceso público)\n   • n exacto: 100 kernels, selección aleatoria con seed=42\n   • Fecha de acceso: 15-enero-2024\n\n② Herramientas y Versiones\n   • GPT-3.5-turbo (OpenAI, enero 2024)\n   • Python 3.11, SciPy 1.11, NumPy 1.26\n   • Hardware: NVIDIA A100, CUDA 12.0\n\n③ Diseño Experimental\n   • Variable independiente: restricciones gramaticales (ON/OFF)\n   • Variable dependiente: tasa de validez sintáctica (%)\n   • Diseño: 2 grupos independientes, n=50 c/u\n\n④ Protocolo de Reproducibilidad\n   • seed=42 fijada antes de cualquier randomización\n   • temperature=0.0 para determinismo en LLM\n   • 5 seeds de verificación: 42, 123, 456, 789, 999\n\n⑤ Métricas y Criterios\n   • Métrica primaria: % kernels que compilan sin errores\n   • Umbral de importancia: d ≥ 0.5 (efecto mediano)\n   • Prueba estadística: t-test o Mann-Whitney U","originalText":"① Dataset y Datos\n   • Fuente: OpenCL Benchmark Suite v2.1 (acceso público)\n   • n exacto: 100 kernels, selección aleatoria con seed=42\n   • Fecha de acceso: 15-enero-2024\n\n② Herramientas y Versiones\n   • GPT-3.5-turbo (OpenAI, enero 2024)\n   • Python 3.11, SciPy 1.11, NumPy 1.26\n   • Hardware: NVIDIA A100, CUDA 12.0\n\n③ Diseño Experimental\n   • Variable independiente: restricciones gramaticales (ON/OFF)\n   • Variable dependiente: tasa de validez sintáctica (%)\n   • Diseño: 2 grupos independientes, n=50 c/u\n\n④ Protocolo de Reproducibilidad\n   • seed=42 fijada antes de cualquier randomización\n   • temperature=0.0 para determinismo en LLM\n   • 5 seeds de verificación: 42, 123, 456, 789, 999\n\n⑤ Métricas y Criterios\n   • Métrica primaria: % kernels que compilan sin errores\n   • Umbral de importancia: d ≥ 0.5 (efecto mediano)\n   • Prueba estadística: t-test o Mann-Whitney U","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#065f46","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":221,"version":1,"versionNonce":222,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"trap_box","x":515,"y":38,"width":375,"height":250,"strokeColor":"#991b1b","backgroundColor":"#fee2e2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":301,"version":1,"versionNonce":302,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"trap_h","x":515,"y":46,"width":375,"height":18,"text":"TRAMPAS COMUNES A EVITAR","originalText":"TRAMPAS COMUNES A EVITAR","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#7f1d1d","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":311,"version":1,"versionNonce":312,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"trap_c","x":523,"y":68,"width":359,"height":212,"text":"✗ Overfitting Accidental\n  Ajustar hiperparámetros DESPUÉS de ver\n  resultados → resultados inflados, no\n  generalizan\n\n✗ Versionitis\n  Cambiar versión del modelo durante\n  experimento → resultados incomparables\n\n✗ Incompletitud de Detalles\n  \"Usamos GPT\" (¿cuál versión? ¿cuándo?)\n  → No reproducible\n\n✗ Cambios Post-hoc\n  Cambiar métricas después de ver datos\n  → sesgo de confirmación\n\n✗ Falta de Seeds\n  Reportar un solo run → no robusto\n\n✗ Cherry-picking\n  Mostrar solo el mejor resultado de\n  varios experimentos → p-hacking","originalText":"✗ Overfitting Accidental\n  Ajustar hiperparámetros DESPUÉS de ver\n  resultados → resultados inflados, no\n  generalizan\n\n✗ Versionitis\n  Cambiar versión del modelo durante\n  experimento → resultados incomparables\n\n✗ Incompletitud de Detalles\n  \"Usamos GPT\" (¿cuál versión? ¿cuándo?)\n  → No reproducible\n\n✗ Cambios Post-hoc\n  Cambiar métricas después de ver datos\n  → sesgo de confirmación\n\n✗ Falta de Seeds\n  Reportar un solo run → no robusto\n\n✗ Cherry-picking\n  Mostrar solo el mejor resultado de\n  varios experimentos → p-hacking","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#991b1b","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":321,"version":1,"versionNonce":322,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.4},

    {"type":"rectangle","id":"diff_box","x":10,"y":300,"width":880,"height":52,"strokeColor":"#2d3e56","backgroundColor":"#dde3ed","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":401,"version":1,"versionNonce":402,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"roundness":{"type":3}},
    {"type":"text","id":"diff_h","x":10,"y":308,"width":880,"height":16,"text":"\"Lo que Hice\" vs. Metodología — La diferencia","originalText":"\"Lo que Hice\" vs. Metodología — La diferencia","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#2d3e56","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":411,"version":1,"versionNonce":412,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"type":"text","id":"diff_c","x":18,"y":326,"width":864,"height":18,"text":"\"Lo que hice\": narrativa cronológica — \"Primero probé X, luego Y, finalmente Z\"\nMetodología: protocolo replicable — \"Se generaron N kernels usando [modelo+versión] con [parámetros], evaluados por [métrica] con análisis [estadístico]\"","originalText":"\"Lo que hice\": narrativa cronológica — \"Primero probé X, luego Y, finalmente Z\"\nMetodología: protocolo replicable — \"Se generaron N kernels usando [modelo+versión] con [parámetros], evaluados por [métrica] con análisis [estadístico]\"","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#2d3e56","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":421,"version":1,"versionNonce":422,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.35},

    {"type":"text","id":"footnote","x":10,"y":362,"width":880,"height":18,"text":"Test de replicabilidad: ¿podría alguien reproducir tu experimento exactamente leyendo solo tu metodología, sin hablar contigo? Si no, falta detalle.","originalText":"Test de replicabilidad: ¿podría alguien reproducir tu experimento exactamente leyendo solo tu metodología, sin hablar contigo? Si no, falta detalle.","fontSize":11,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"center","verticalAlign":"top","strokeColor":"#475569","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":501,"version":1,"versionNonce":502,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":null,"lineHeight":1.25}
